public interface BalancedBTree<E extends Comparable<? super E>> extends BinaryTree<E>
A height-balanced binary search tree. This interface does not introduce any new methods beyond BinaryTree, but its use indicates that the implementing tree class is self-balancing. As a result, all methods of the tree are expected to run in O(logn) time.
